<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="1671543" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix"><strong>在Quora上看到一个句子很符合题主的问题，但在《道德经》上没有找到类似的原文。</strong><br><strong><em>----</em></strong><br><strong><em>"If you are depressed, you are living in the past. If you are anxious you are living in the future. If you are at peace, you are living in the present." - </em>Lao Tzu</strong><br><img src="http://pic3.zhimg.com/6f915bd1220f6b2230dc09662697efc2_b.jpg" data-rawheight="480" data-rawwidth="480" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="480" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/6f915bd1220f6b2230dc09662697efc2_r.jpg">
<a href="/question/23724864/answer/25546882" class="toggle-expand">显示全部</a>
